  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>. Minimum Degree in Accountancy or equivalent</p><p>2. Min. at least 5years in handling full set of accounts independently</p><p>3. Accounting knowledge with hands on experience<br /></p><p>Responsibilities:-</p><p>1. Handle fullset of accounts, prepare management accounts and audit schedules</p><p>2. Review subsidiary accounts and analyse variance</p><p>3. Liaise with external auditor on audit matters and audit schedules</p><p>4. Experience in using internet banking for payment</p><p>5.Knowledge of payroll processing with Times Payroll</p><p>6. Familiar with Microsoft 365 Dynamic Business</p><p>7. Proficient in Ms Excel</p><p>8. Ad hoc duties as assigned</p><p>Looking for applicant can start work immediately.</p><p>Working hours: 8.30am to 6pm ( Mon to Friday)</p><p>Lunch : 1pm to 1.45pm</p>",
